@c TREE_REDUCE ACCEPTS A SET OR LIST AS AN ARGUMENT, BUT RREDUCE AND LREDUCE WANT ONLY LISTS; STRANGE
@deffn {Funci@'on} tree_reduce (@var{F}, @var{s})
